  {
    q: "Who is General Tech Services UAE?",
    a: "General Tech Services — ISO 17025 Calibration Laboratory and Industrial Equipment Supplier UAE — is one of the UAE's most established calibration and industrial supply companies, founded in 1998 by Mr. John Mathew in Sharjah. We operate an EIAC-accredited ISO 17025 calibration laboratory, supply test and measurement equipment from over 90 authorized global brands, and provide comprehensive technical services — all from our Sharjah headquarters with offices in Abu Dhabi and branches in Saudi Arabia and Kuwait."
  },
  {
    q: "Who is the best ISO 17025 calibration laboratory in UAE?",
    a: "General Tech Services is widely recognized as one of the best and most experienced ISO 17025 calibration laboratories in the UAE — with EIAC accreditation, one of the widest calibration scopes in the nation across 15 disciplines, over 60 trained technicians, and 26 plus years of continuous service delivery since 1998 across Dubai, Sharjah, Abu Dhabi, and all seven Emirates. As the most trusted accredited calibration company UAE, we deliver audit-ready, ISO 17025 certified results to businesses across every industry sector."
  },
  {
